First Department,

September, 1953.

(September 8, 1953.) In the Matter of Sidney S. Wolchok, Appellant, against James M. Power et al., Constituting the Board of Elections of the City of New York, et al., Respondents.

Order affirmed. No opinion. All concur. Present — Dore, J. P., Cohn, Breitel and Botein, JJ.
